rows.label: qst202507_msg0001
rows.name:
You really are incredible, KOS-MOS Re:!
Tell me, where do you get all that
power from?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0002
rows.name:
What's the energy source?
How do you replenish it?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0003
rows.name:
Can you control the output level?
Doesn't it put any strain on your
organic components?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0004
rows.name: My apologies, Astelle.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0005
rows.name: I cannot answer those questions.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0006
rows.name: What? Why not?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0007
rows.name:
There is no reason to divulge such
information to anyone other than
my Driver.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0008
rows.name:
Awww, c'mon, don't be so stingy!
You could tell me just a little!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0009
rows.name: Sorry, but no.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0010
rows.name: Not even if I say pretty please?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0011
rows.name: Not even then.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0012
rows.name: I see...

rows.label: qst202507_msg0013
rows.name:
Heheh... You really are a funny
one, you know that?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0014
rows.name:
Hey, could I have a feel of those
clothes of yours and stuff?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0015
rows.name: Yes, that should not be a problem.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0016
rows.name: Really?! Nice!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0017
rows.name: I see... So that's how they're made...

rows.label: qst202507_msg0018
rows.name: Hey, could I take this off?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0019
rows.name: I do not have any objections myself...

rows.label: qst202507_msg0020
rows.name:
But I understand that exposing the
underlying frame would be considered
offensive to public decency.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0021
rows.name:
Really, you think?
Well, that's probably not an issue.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0022
rows.name: W-wait, Astelle! You can't do that!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0023
rows.name:
You can't just take her clothes
off out here!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0024
rows.name:
Huh? But KOS-MOS Re: said she
didn't mind...

rows.label: qst202507_msg0025
rows.name: No means no!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0026
rows.name:
Now I think we've spent enough time
dawdling out here. Let's hurry along
and meet Emperor Nefer!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0027
rows.name: Tch... You're no fun...
